description:
Small, fully furnished one bedroom apartment in a Harlem pre-war brownstone.

The apartment, Kitchen and bathroom are fully equipped with everything you might need. 60" TV with netflix, 4K monitor for your laptop, recliner couch, massage chair.

I am  looking to rent out my apartment while I'm away for the month of March. 30 discount for renting a whole month.

Closest subway station is the 2,3 only 3 blocks away. Followed by the A,C,D then the 4,5,6.
name: Small artsy apartment in a New York brownstone
